Zeenat Name Moon Sign

The names that start with the letter “Z” falls under the “Uttara Bhadrapada” nakshatra, whose ruling lord is planet Saturn and the numerology is 7, which is ruled by Ketu. This letter is associated with the “Pisces” moon sign, which is ruled by two planets Neptune and Jupiter. People with names starting with the letter Z are extremely courageous and hence don’t get afraid of challenges and stand up for what they believe in. They can be fantastic in planning and strategizing. They are charismatic and have great common sense and understanding. These people are pragmatic, logical and spontaneous.

Zeenat Name Personality

The moon sign Pisces is one of the most compassionate moon signs. They are empathetic, creative and dream big. They may also come across as someone who is an escapist. Their preferred career path is in healing or counselling. Pisces Moon is not afraid of sacrificing and putting others' choices and preferences first. They are dreamy and can often get overwhelmed by the reality. It is essential for people with the Pisces moon sign to say no to people at times, as people can easily take them for a ride. Pisces moon sign should also seek help whenever required and not hesitate.
